&lt;p&gt;1. 서류 전형 → 2. 화상 인터뷰 → 3. 직무 인터뷰 → 4. 컬쳐핏 인터뷰 및 레퍼런스 체크 → 5. 처우협의 →&amp;nbsp; 6. 최종 합격 및 입사&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong data-stringify-type=&quot;bold&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;c-emoji c-emoji__medium c-emoji--inline&quot; data-qa=&quot;emoji&quot; data-sk=&quot;tooltip_parent&quot;&gt;👉&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://daangn.notion.site/f371d4e1412d422e95b343117d93521a&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-stringify-type=&quot;bold&quot;&gt;당근 합류 여정 가이드 바로가기&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong data-stringify-type=&quot;bold&quot;&gt;(🔗)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
